tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE robotics_club_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_name VARCHAR(50),
    member_email VARCHAR(100),
    code_snippet TEXT,
    programming_language VARCHAR(50),
    error_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE code_snippets (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_id INT,
    language TEXT,
    code TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE errors (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_id INT,
    error_description TEXT,
    error_solution TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
